ic\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-title\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 900; font-size: 20px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">FAQ</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Q:Can I use this for my ps4??</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">A:Yes, it works with PS4, but not with Xbox.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Q:Does it pick up background noise</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">A:Yes, any microphone picks up background noise, espeically for those sensitive one. You can isolate most of the noise by keeping environment quiet (use in a closet for perfect result) and turning down the on-body control &amp; input level on computer.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Q:does it record stereo voice?</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">A:It\'s mono microphone, though it only matters when you use it with Mac. For Windows computer, which will split the audio signal into left and right channel automatically, then you won\'t have any problem of recording stereo sound. But whatever computer you use, you still can do some easy post-production to make recording stereo.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Q:can this be put onto a boom arm?</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">A:Yes, any standard boom arm which come with 3/8” Female to 5/8” Male adapter will be compatible. After screwing the adaptor to the mic mount, then you can install it on boom arm.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Q:What latency can I get with it with an on board audio card?</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_text\">\r\n<p class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\" style=\"text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: \'OpenSans\'; color: #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">A:When you do some monitoring through the headphone jack of computer, I\'m afraid that the worest delay would be around 300-500 ms.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detailmodule_image\"><img class=\"detail-desc-decorate-image\" src=\"//ae01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB14wl9Xhz1gK0jSZSgq6yvwpXaO.jpg\" /><img class=\"detail-desc-decorate-image\" src=\"//ae01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1Eex8XkT2gK0jSZPcq6AKkpXar.jpg\" /><img class=\"detail-desc-decorate-image\" src=\"//ae01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1V.04XkH0gK0jSZPiq6yvapXaE.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<script>window.adminAccountId=234591151;</script>','Металлический конденсаторный микрофон Fifine с USB для ноутбука, Windows, кардиоидный Студийный микрофон для записи голоса, YouTube-K669','','publish','open','closed','','fifine-metal-usb-condenser-recording-microphone-for-laptop-windows-cardioid-studio-recording-vocals-voice-overyoutube-k669','','','2020-07-20 21:50:13','2020-07-20 18:50:13','',0,'http://f0455068.xsph.ru/wordpress/product/fifine-metal-usb-condenser-recording-microphone-for-laptop-windows-cardioid-studio-recording-vocals-voice-overyoutube-k669/',0,'product','',0),(95,1,'2020-07-20 21:50:00','2020-07-20 18:50:00','<div class=\"detailmodule_html\">\n<div class=\"detail-desc-decorate-richtext\">\n\n<span data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2g0o.detail.1000023.i3.554646a0VmvmPE\"><strong data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2g0o.detail.1000023.i0.554646a0VmvmPE\">①</strong> <strong>Подключи и играй USB</strong>-микрофон, который подключается к твоему компьютеру или ноутбуку напрямую через USB-порт (работа с Mac и Windows Vista, XP), без труда записывая музыку или подкаст. (◆◆ Не совместимо с Xbox и телефонами ◆◆)</span>\n<p align=\"justify\"><b>②</b>Прочный дизайнерский корпус со штативом stabletripod stand пригодится, ко